					Latest Key Developments (Source: Significant Developments)




Revoil Petroleum sales 100 pct its units shares of ARISTON EEPN
Friday, 19 May 2017 11:23am EDT 
May 19 (Reuters) - REVOIL PETROLEUM COMPANY SA REVR.AT::ANNOUNCES THAT IT HAS PROCEEDED TO THE SALE OF THE SHARES OF 100 PERCENT SUBSIDIARY OF ARISTON EEPN OPERATING IN SEAFARING.SAYS THE SALE PRICE AMOUNTED TO US $ 185,000.AFTER SALE OF ITS UNIT, IS RELIEVED OF A LOSS-MAKING ACTIVITY THAT HAS BURDENED ITS EFFECTS IN RECENT YEARS. 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum's unit Ariston increases its share capital by 2.2 million euros
Tuesday, 16 May 2017 09:44am EDT 
May 16 (Reuters) - REVOIL PETROLEUM COMPANY SA REVR.AT::ITS UNIT ARISTON INCREASES ITS SHARE CAPITAL BY EUR 2.2 MILLION BY ISSUING 728,670 NEW REGISTERED SHARES WITH VALUE OF EUR 3.0 EACH.SHARE CAPITAL OF ARISTON AFTER ABOVE INCREASE WILL AMOUNT TO EUR 33.4 MILLION DIVIDED INTO 11,119,004 OF EUR 3.0 VALUE EACH SHARE. 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum Company sales storage facilities in the area of KAVALA worth 15 million euros
Friday, 12 May 2017 10:40am EDT 
May 12 (Reuters) - REVOIL PETROLEUM COMPANY SA REVR.AT ::SALES STORAGE FACILITIES IN THE AREA OF KAVALA WORTH EUR 15 MILLION. 
			
Full Article





Revoil sees an increase in consumption in existing network and enlargement through range of products
Thursday, 13 Apr 2017 11:19am EDT 
Revoil Petroleum Company SA :Says for 2017 it focuses in increase consumption in existing network and enlargement through range of products in the network. 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum FY 2016 net loss widens to 29.4 million euros
Thursday, 13 Apr 2017 10:12am EDT 
Revoil Petroleum Company SA : FY 2016 turnover at 646.0 million euros ($685.73 million) versus 656.3 million euros year ago . FY 2016 net loss at of 29.4 million euros versus loss 3.0 million euros year ago . FY 2016 EBITDA loss at 17.9 million euros versus EBITDA at 8.9 million euros year ago .Net cash on Dec. 31, 2016 at 6.2 million euros versus 4.3 million euros year ago. 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum Company Sa will pay no dividend for FY 2016
Wednesday, 12 Apr 2017 10:59am EDT 
Revoil Petroleum Company SA :Says it will pay no dividend for FY 2016. 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum unit sells ship for 2.5 mln USD
Thursday, 9 Feb 2017 10:42am EST 
Revoil Petroleum Company SA :Says its Ariston unit sold its Blue Angel ship of 44,950 tons capacity for 2.5 million usd. 
			
Full Article





Revoil H1 net loss at 2.36 mln euros vs 1.19 mln loss last year
Thursday, 29 Sep 2016 11:23am EDT 
Revoil Petroleum Company S.A. : H1 net loss at 2.36 mln euros versus 1.17 mln euro loss in H1 2015 . H1 EBITDA profit 24.9 pct down to 3.3 mln euros . H1 sales fall 11.8 pct to 293.8 mln euros (Reporting by Athens newsroom) ((michele.kambas@thomsonreuters.com;)). 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum Co SA incorporates 7 new gas stations to its network
Friday, 8 Apr 2016 11:46am EDT 
Revoil Petroleum Co SA:Incorporates 7 new gas stations to its network. 
			
Full Article





Revoil Petroleum Co SA installs new stock control system
Wednesday, 19 Aug 2015 07:17am EDT 
Revoil Petroleum Co SA:Completes installation of the inflow-outflow stock control system in its Aspropyrgos and Chios storage facilities.Says the new system will fight illegal trading, is put in place after the ministry's new legislation. 
			
Full Article





