                                                Revoil Petroleum Company SA
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Revoil Petroleum Company SA operates within the Gasoline service stations sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Revoil Petroleum Company SA with three other
	gasoline service stations in Europe:
		
	Makpetrol AD Skopje
	
		of Macedonia
		(2016
	sales of 16.47 billion Denar [US$311.45  million]
		),
	
	Villars Holding SA
	
		of Switzerland
		(79.37 million Swiss Francs [US$83.46  million]
		), and
	
	Petrol a.d. Banja Luka
	
		which is
		
		based in Bosnia
		(203.91 million Bosnian Convertible Marks [US$121.52  million]
		).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	
		During the year ended December of 2016, sales at
		Revoil Petroleum Company SA were 645.98 million Euro (US$758.19 million).
	
		This
		
			is
		
			a
			
			decrease of 1.6%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 656.25 million Euro.
	

	





 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










