Profile data is unavailable for this security.About the companyRevoil Petroleum Company SA is a Greece-based company engaged in the trade of petroleum products. The Company's products include different kinds of liquid gas, such as unleaded petrol of 95 and 100 octane, lead replacement petrol of 96 octane and other petroleum products, such as diesel, heating oil, kerosene and fuel oil. In addition the Company sells a range of Revoil branded lubricants. The Company owns and runs liquid fuel storage facilities, as well as operates refueling branches for its distribution of fuel. The Company's segments are: Petroleum Sector-Marketing of Biofuels; Lubricant Sector, and Investment Sector in Pontopore Shipping. The Company operates through a network of more than 500 service stations. Revoil Petroleum Company SA's subsidiary is Revoil SA of Trading Biofuels.Revenue in EUR (TTM)645.98mNet income in EUR-29.42mIncorporated--Employees184.00LocationRevoil Petroleum Company SAKapodistriou 5, VariATHINA 166 72GreeceGRCPhone+30 2 108976000Fax+30 2 108974943Websitehttp://www.revoil.gr/More ▼ 
Income statement (EUR)Year on year Revoil Petroleum Company SA's net income fell 866.47% from a loss of 3.04m to a larger loss of 29.42m despite relatively flat revenues. A contributing factor has been an increase in the selling, general and administrative costs as a percentage of sales from 2.49% to 2.74%.FT Lexicon{0}{0}{2}{0}{0}{2}For more information, visit the FT LexiconLexicon on this pageExplore our toolsAlertsData archivePortfolioWorld marketsEquities screenerFunds overview



